# Component Catalog — {{ solution.display_name }}

This document provides an architectural overview of all software components defined in the blueprint for **{{ workspace.display_name }}**.

Components are grouped by functional role. The term *component* is used as a generic umbrella; each entry has a specific `kind` that determines its role and local folder group.

## Terminology

| Kind | Folder Group | Description |
| --- | --- | --- |
| `service` | `services/` | Backend service or microservice |
| `app` | `apps/` | Standalone runnable application (frontend, admin portal, mobile) |
| `job` | `jobs/` | Scheduled, batch, Spark, ETL, analytics, or background job |
| `connector` | `connectors/` | Integration adapter for external systems, Kafka, APIs |
| `library` | `libraries/` | Shared code library used by multiple repositories |

