## Communication Topology

- **Docker Compose Setup**: Containerized services communicate inside the Compose network (`infra/compose/compose.local.yml`).
- **Local Debugging Override**: A service under active debugging uses `host.docker.internal:<port>` to connect from other containers to your local IDE process.
- **Isolated Databases**: Each database-owning service gets its own isolated container (`<service-name>-db`).
